<emphasis box="[1309,1437,224,247]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="547">MesΟsΟma.</emphasis>
Length 
<quantity box="[239,357,260,285]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.25" pageId="4" pageNumber="547" unit="mm" value="0.425">0.425 mm</quantity>
. Relative measurements: forewing width 26, proportions of veins as in Fig. 1; hindwing width 10; distribution of setae at base of wing as in Fig. 1; mid tibia 22; midtibial spur 5. 
<emphasis box="[1096,1220,296,319]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="547">MetasΟma.</emphasis>
Length 
<quantity box="[1315,1431,295,320]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.75" pageId="4" pageNumber="547" unit="mm" value="0.575">0.575 mm</quantity>
, ovipositor not protruding.
</paragraph>
